<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, date=no, address=no, email=no">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-KfkfwYDsLkIlwQp6LFnl8zNdLGxu9YAA1QvwINks4PhcElQSvqcyVLLD9aMhXd13uQjoXtEKNosOWaZqXgel0g=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Neulis Alt';
            src: url('/public/font/NeulisAlt-Regular.woff2') format('woff2'),
                url('/public/font/NeulisAlt-Regular.woff') format('woff'),
                url('/public/font/NeulisAlt-Regular.ttf') format('truetype');
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Neulis Alt', sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .email-content {
            padding: 48px;
            background-color: #e6ffeb;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .email-content h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .email-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .otp-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #32b338;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-content {
                padding: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-content">
            <p>Hey,</p>
            <h1><%= first_name %> <%= last_name %></h1>
            <p>A request to verify your email was received for the address: <strong><%= email %></strong>.</p>
            <p>Use the following OTP to verify your email and complete the login process:</p>
            <a href="#" class="otp-button"><%= otp %></a>
            <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
